# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── secrets
# §0: credentials never touch the repo. .env.example is the committed template.
# `.env.*` catches .env.local / .env.prod / .env.bak too — a stray backup of a filled-in
# .env is the usual way a token reaches a public repo.
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
token.json
credentials.json

# Generated by scripts/make-vps-paste.py: holds a live NIM key and bot token in plain text,
# for pasting into a VPS web console. Delete it once the VPS is up.
vps-paste.txt

# Your real class timetable: it says where you physically are, every week. The repo ships
# config/timetable.example.yaml — copy it to config/timetable.yaml and keep yours local.
config/timetable.yaml

# Stray CVs/resumes/certificates dropped in the project ROOT. The master CV belongs in
# data/cv/ (ignored below); this is belt-and-braces, because `git add -A` on a public repo
# would otherwise publish your phone number and home address. Root-only: docs/ is unaffected.
/*.pdf
/*.docx
/*.doc

# The Gmail token lives here on the droplet (see secrets/README.md). Ignore the contents but
# keep the README, so the directory — and the instructions — survive a clone.
secrets/*
!secrets/README.md

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────── runtime data
# Calvin's actual content: master CV and tailored variants, course notes, lecture audio,
# generated prep/cram PDFs, the pre-migration SQLite file. Personal — none of it belongs
# in git.
#
# Ignore the CONTENTS but keep the directories, via a tracked .gitkeep. They must exist in a
# fresh clone: docker-compose bind-mounts ./data and ./logs, and Docker creates a missing
# bind source as ROOT — the container runs as uid 1000 and dies with
# `PermissionError: /app/logs/agentos.log`. A .gitkeep means `git clone` makes them, owned
# by whoever cloned, and the mount just works. Everything below them is re-created on demand
# (core/config.py, core/pdf.py, skills/lecture_capture.py, ...).
data/*
!data/.gitkeep
logs/*
!logs/.gitkeep
*.log
agentos-backup-*.tar.gz
agentos.sql

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── python
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
.venv/
venv/
.python/
.test-tmp-*/
.test-*/
*.egg-info/
.pytest_cache/
.ruff_cache/
.mypy_cache/

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── docker
# Local-only compose overrides (ports, mounts) — every box differs.
docker-compose.override.yml

# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── tooling
.agents/
.claude/
.kilo/
.idea/
.vscode/

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── os
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
